Rolling-window backtest (walk-forward CV) — compute RMSE, MAE, MAPE, directional accuracy, and excess return when using model-driven portfolio vs benchmark.

Use portfolio-level evaluation (simulated optimized portfolio using predicted returns) to check real advisory impact (this is key for ConSaaS credibility).

